OL,7,FPolice began gathering information
OL,8,Fabout visitors to Stephen Lawrence's
OL,9,Fbereaved parents the day after his
OL,10,Fmurder, a public inquiry has been told.
OL,12,FIn an opening statement on behalf of
OL,13,FStephen's father Neville, Ifeanyi
OL,14,FOdogwu claimed the Met had put the
OL,15,FLawrences under surveillance almost
OL,16,Fimmediately after Stephen's murder.
