OL,7,FHe was speaking at the latest stage of
OL,8,Fthe public inquiry into undercover
OL,9,Fpolicing, which is looking at the
OL,10,Factivities of the Met's Special
OL,11,FDemonstration Squad (SDS) between 1993
OL,12,Fand 2007.
OL,14,F"While the Lawrences sought justice,
OL,15,Fstate power turned on the family," he
OL,16,Fsaid.
