OL,4,CLawrence campaign 'almost at once'
OL,5,Cafter murder
OL,7,F"From the earliest days after
OL,8,FStephen's murder, the Metropolitan
OL,9,FPolice, through Special Branch's SDS,
OL,10,Fbegan collecting and circulating
OL,11,Fintimate information about the
OL,12,FLawrences and those assisting them.
OL,14,F"That activity continued for years and
OL,15,Freached into the Macpherson Inquiry
OL,16,Fitself."
OL,18,FHe told chairman Sir John Mitting:
OL,19,F"Surveillance started almost at once,
OL,20,Fthe day after the murder."
