OL,7,FIt is "truly abhorrent and shocking"
OL,8,Fthat information about the couple was
OL,9,Fpassed to officers in the Met's team
OL,10,Ftaking part in the Macpherson Inquiry
OL,11,Finto the mishandled investigation into
OL,12,FStephen's death, he said.
OL,14,FMr Lawrence said in a statement to the
OL,15,Finquiry: "The implication, that we
OL,16,Fwere somehow the ones to watch, was as
OL,17,Fperverse as it was offensive.
