OL,7,FThere were also false claims about
OL,8,FNeville Lawrence's finances, including
OL,9,Fthat he was being given #500,000 by BT
OL,10,Fto set up a civil rights organisation,
OL,11,Fand that he was considering running
OL,12,Ffor London mayor and had received
OL,13,F#500,000 from Lottery funding.
OL,15,FNone of the details gathered would
OL,16,Fhave helped prevent public disorder,
OL,17,Fthe inquiry was told, which was the
OL,18,Fsupposed aim of the SDS.
