OL,7,F"The undercover policing of the
OL,8,FLawrences occurred at times of the
OL,9,Futmost sensitivity, while resources
OL,10,Fshould have been focused on finding
OL,11,FStephen's killers, and during
OL,12,FMacpherson," Mr Odogwu said.
OL,14,F"An intrusion in such highly sensitive
OL,15,Fperiods requires a compelling case,
OL,16,Fand there is none."
