OL,7,FIn his opening statement to the
OL,8,FUndercover Policing Inquiry on
OL,9,FTuesday, Rajiv Menon KC said racist
OL,10,Fviolence, including murders in the
OL,11,F1980s and 1990s, could have been
OL,12,Fprevented if police had effectively
OL,13,Ftargeted far right extremists and
OL,14,Fracist criminal groups.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/13
