OL,3,CPolice began spying on Stephen
OL,4,CLawrence campaign 'almost at once'
OL,5,Cafter murder
OL,7,F"Mr Brooks finds it profoundly
OL,8,Fdisturbing that the police were spying
OL,9,Fon him and other victims of racist
OL,10,Fviolence but not, as far as he is
OL,11,Faware, on well-known racist criminal
OL,12,Fgroups who were committing serious
OL,13,Fviolent crimes," Mr Menon said.
OL,15,FIn 1993 the secret Met Special
OL,16,FDemonstration Squad (SDS) viewed anti-
OL,17,Fracist campaigners as more of a threat
OL,18,Fthan far-right activists and
OL,19,Fperpetrators of racist violence, Mr
OL,20,FMenon told the hearing.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@PO]
