OL,7,F"It is precisely this perverse
OL,8,Fanalysis that led to Mr Brooks, the
OL,9,Fsurviving victim of a racist murder,
OL,10,Fbeing mistreated by the police and
OL,11,Fspied on by the SDS, whilst Stephen
OL,12,FLawrence's murderers walked free.
OL,14,F"It was not until 2010 that the police
OL,15,Ffinally charged two of those
OL,16,Fresponsible with murder.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
